          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>普通攻击</color>\n造成1点 <color=#99ffff>冰元素伤害</color> 。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "雾虚摇唤",
        "title": "雾虚摇唤",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/1a979041a9881649ba69332b20dd5820_4421361652799067673.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>元素战技</color>\n造成1点 <color=#99ffff>冰元素伤害</color> ，召唤 <color=#ffffff>冰萤</color> 。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "冰枝白花",
        "title": "冰枝白花",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/8d60085e1f79ee9a2bb87006d7f2d32c_1352391964926778194.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>元素爆发</color>\n造成5点 <color=#99ffff>冰元素伤害</color> ，本角色附着 <color=#99ffff>冰元素</color> ，生成 <color=#ffffff>流萤护罩</color> 。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "冰萤",
        "title": "冰萤",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_8332858692182745968.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>召唤物</color>\n<color=#ffffff>结束阶段：</color> 造成1点 <color=#99ffff>冰元素伤害</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>可用次数：2</color> （可叠加，最多叠加到3次）\n<color=#ffffff>愚人众 · 冰萤术士「普通攻击」后：</color> 此牌 <color=#ffffff>可用次数</color> +1。\n<color=#ffffff>愚人众 · 冰萤术士受到发生元素反应的伤害后：</color> 此牌 <color=#ffffff>可用次数</color> -1。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": [],
        "talentImg": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/1467dd7dd3fec80047e77cc996621508_8264366558691582431.png"
      },
      {
        "key": "冰元素伤害",
        "title": "冰元素伤害",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/88072335/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_3596343439023884151.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "附着冰元素，可发生元素反应：\n【 <color=#99ffff>冰元素</color> + <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>融化</color> ：本伤害+2\n【 <color=#99ffff>冰元素</color> + <color=#ffacff>雷元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>超导</color> ：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害\n【 <color=#99ffff>冰元素</color> + <color=#80c0ff>水元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>冻结</color> ：本伤害+1，使目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "规则术语",
        "title": "规则术语",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/88072335/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_6983108032915946298.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ece5d8>物理伤害</color>\n物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。\n<color=#ece5d8>可用次数</color>\n此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次 <color=#ffffff>可用次数</color> ；\n<color=#ffffff>可用次数</color> 耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。\n<color=#ece5d8>流萤护罩</color>\n<color=#ffd780>出战状态</color>\n为我方出战角色提供 <color=#ffffff>1点护盾</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>创建时：</color> 如果我放场上存在 <color=#ffffff>冰萤</color> ，则额外提供其 <color=#ffffff>可用次数</color> 的 <color=#ffffff>护盾</color> 。（最多额外提供3点 <color=#ffffff>护盾</color> ）\n<color=#ece5d8>护盾</color>\n此护盾所保护的角色受到伤害时，将会消耗护盾来抵消伤害。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      }
    ],
